<div class="core-journal-description"><div property="isPartOf" typeof="Periodical"><span property="name">RadioGraphics</span></div><div class="core-enumeration"><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationVolume">Volume <span property="volumeNumber">28</span></span> • <span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">7</span></span> • <span property="datePublished">Nov 1 2008</span></div><div class="core-pagination"><span class="heading">Pages</span>: <span class="content"><span property="pageStart">1951</span> - <span property="pageEnd">1962</span></span></div><div class="core-pmid"><span class="heading">PubMed</span>: <a class="content" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19001651/" property="sameAs" target="_blank" title="Link to PubMed">19001651</a></div></div></div></section><section class="core-copyright"><h4>Copyright</h4><div role="paragraph">© RSNA, 2008.</div></section><section class="core-history"><h4>History</h4><div><b class="core-label">Published online</b>: Nov 1 2008</div></section><section class="core-permissions"><h4>Permissions</h4><div>Request permissions for this article.</div><div><a class="btn" href="https://marketplace.copyright.com/rs-ui-web/mp/search/all/10.1148%2Frg.287085031">Request Permissions</a></div></section><section property="keywords"><h4>Keywords</h4><ol><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=CBD+%3D+common+bile+duct&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">CBD = common bile duct</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=ERCP+%3D+endoscopic+retrograde+cholangiopancreatography&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">ERCP = endoscopic retrograde cholangiopancreatography</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=ETL+%3D+echo+train+length&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">ETL = echo train length</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=FSE+%3D+fast+spin-echo&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">FSE = fast spin-echo</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=MIP+%3D+maximum-intensity-projection&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">MIP = maximum-intensity-projection</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=PBJ+%3D+pancreaticobiliary+junction&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">PBJ = pancreaticobiliary junction</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=PSC+%3D+primary+sclerosing+cholangitis&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">PSC = primary sclerosing cholangitis</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=RF+%3D+radiofrequency&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">RF = radiofrequency</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=SNR+%3D+signal-to-noise+ratio&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">SNR = signal-to-noise ratio</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=TSE+%3D+turbo+spin-echo&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">TSE = turbo spin-echo</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=2D+%3D+two-dimensional&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">2D = two-dimensional</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=3D+%3D+three-dimensional&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">3D = three-dimensional</a></li></ol></section><section class="core-article-notes"><h4>Notes</h4><div role="paragraph">Pediatric MR cholangiopancreatography is discussed and illustrated in terms of basic principles, types of sequences used, factors affecting image quality, potential challenges and possible solutions, and current clinical applications.</div></section></section><section id="tab-contributors" role="tabpanel"><h3>Authors</h3><section class="core-authors"><h4>Affiliations</h4><div id="con1" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Govind B.</span> <span property="familyName">Chavhan</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD, DNB</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Department of Diagnostic Imaging, The Hospital For Sick Children and University of Toronto, 555 University Ave, Toronto, ON, Canada M5G 1X8. Presented as an education exhibit at the 2007 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received February 19, 2008; revision requested March 18 and received March 31; accepted April 9. All authors have no financial relationships to disclose.</span></div></div><div class="core-author-link"><a href="/authored-by/Chavhan/Govind+B" rel="nofollow">View all articles by this author</a></div></div></div><div id="con2" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Paul S.</span> <span property="familyName">Babyn</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Department of Diagnostic Imaging, The Hospital For Sick Children and University of Toronto, 555 University Ave, Toronto, ON, Canada M5G 1X8. Presented as an education exhibit at the 2007 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received February 19, 2008; revision requested March 18 and received March 31; accepted April 9. All authors have no financial relationships to disclose.</span></div></div><div class="core-author-link"><a href="/authored-by/Babyn/Paul+S" rel="nofollow">View all articles by this author</a></div></div></div><div id="con3" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">David</spa